{"tid":719091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"世盃直播時球迷強吻 女記者「靚閃」兼霸氣鬧爆","createTime":"2018-06-27T07:41:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T09:18:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"54ac151c14ff783684b259272f4c6c98a38d0d3d","tid":719091,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:41:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180627/20433085\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180627%2F20433085&d=q%2F0ocy0U8FGeelLTiruMvIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=b1ddf667\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180627%2F20433085&h=ea7eaf1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180627/20433085</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月27日 <br />\n<br />\n世盃直播時球迷強吻<br />\n女記者「靚閃」兼霸氣鬧爆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一位在俄羅斯報道世界盃消息的巴西女記者，鏡頭前被一名男球迷「突襲」企圖強吻，她及時避開，還教訓對方一頓。<br />\n<br />\n朱利婭．吉馬良斯（Julia Guimaraes）周日在葉卡捷琳堡為巴西環球電視網（TV Globo）報道日本對塞內加爾的比賽，突然一名男子入鏡，吻向朱利婭面頰，朱利婭意識到「狼男」正從旁走近，立即閃身一避。<br />\n<br />\n狼男博懵不成，迅即閃開，卻免不了朱利婭連珠炮發的教訓，叫那位俄羅斯人「不要再這樣對女性好嗎？尊重啊」。聽到身在鏡頭外的男子連聲以「對不起對不起，好的好的」回應。<br />\n<br />\n朱利婭後來說，今次已是第二次在俄羅斯被球迷企圖強吻。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n巴塞寧要難民唔要遊客　推高房租、搶資源大叫怕怕<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n【動畫】英格蘭球迷去到俄羅斯　驚覺帶漏飛好揼心"},{"pid":"190f2ceae9a287bbc26780c5c60b2949e9be040e","tid":719091,"uid":135336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:44:24.000Z","msg":"香港女記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34fd5c7e0e1519c1f680d1042734cfa507e49c1a","tid":719091,"uid":63950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:58:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dfb7c3b022e8ee18279d857ee53907718d35cd8f","tid":719091,"uid":125168,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTi